{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1395191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只要它的存储介质可以随便读就不可能做到这种事情。关键是要放在特定的硬盘里", "timestamp": 1617619642, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395279, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "飞书会不会可以", "timestamp": 1617620342, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395309, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在pdf里面放一个外链图片，只要打开pdf就自动加载，在图片服务器做手脚", "timestamp": 1617620611, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395329, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不联网就没用了", "timestamp": 1617620799, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395339, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那别人随便截个屏就破解了", "timestamp": 1617620851, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395361, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那是不是要是只能联网在线阅读，就有可能实现呢？有没有这样的app", "timestamp": 1617621188, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395364, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者网页", "timestamp": 1617621204, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395385, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 一般来讲，从服务器上请求的文件，都要在本地缓存。对于网页（web）来说，你能看见的东西都不是秘密。那么余下的选择就只有原生应用了。如果应用自身对于所有缓存都加密，那么是可以防止文件复制的。但有一点还是防不住，就是摄屏。应用自身永远无法防止从显示设备之外对文件进行拷贝。", "timestamp": 1617621466, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395388, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "简而言之，你想让别人看见，那么就要有一个显示屏，那么对这个显示屏拍照就可以破解任何此类安全措施", "timestamp": 1617621509, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395443, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这种级别的保密基本上只能依靠硬件。比如说，文件放在仅有一个的硬盘里，硬盘进行全盘加密。解密时除了输入口令还要记录硬盘连接的设备的唯一序列号。如果序列号不可读或不在许可范围内就锁定硬盘。", "timestamp": 1617621921, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395456, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般笔记本电脑的BIOS都是有一个唯一序列号的。手机的话有IMEI。台式机应该也类似。只有获取序列号才允许查看文件，这恐怕是唯一的方法", "timestamp": 1617622014, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395515, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 好的，谢谢Alice！", "timestamp": 1617622714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "突然发现，adobe dc好像有一个追踪功能\n", "timestamp": 1617624705, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395718, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cy，adobe理论是可以的，但是我没用过，一个是adobe中国好像没服务器，一个是好像必须得对方也用了注册过的adobe，还有。。。我买不起正版的adobe，365美元", "timestamp": 1617625184, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "又查了查，好像Maipdf也有这个功能，可以设置阅读次数和时长", "timestamp": 1617627447, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395866, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273919, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是还不知道安全性如何\n", "timestamp": 1617627460, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 273919, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "技术问\n有没有那种能追溯都谁看了这个pdf的软件", "timestamp": 